{"tid":494473,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"不再聯繫","createTime":"2017-12-09T15:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T13:46:42.000Z","uid":84070,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dbc1e900da66a61b4db4dcef0a44a32036eb12af","tid":494473,"uid":84070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:57:30.000Z","msg":"我和你斷了聯繫　不代表我不想你<br />\n走到哪裡還是會有惦記　<br />\n<br />\n就黎又離開香港<br />\n結果都係冇再搵你<br />\n<br />\n連登成日有巴絲問點唔再搵一個人<br />\n其實當對方永遠唔再搵你<br />\n次次都係你搵佢既時候慢慢你就自然會心淡唔想再搵佢<br />\n<br />\n#星期六叫春  #送上歌一首<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4YTaoR7nO28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4YTaoR7nO28&d=rJjrve1ULVWJd0Foy4hClLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=0569b233\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4YTaoR7nO28</a>"},{"pid":"b88734d558e32649f6554dc13940a4d86f664817","tid":494473,"uid":77774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T16:05:13.000Z","msg":"啱呀 揾到好攰了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a005df3067d51f50a6346e1676ee71d13bf8204b","tid":494473,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"#############################"},{"pid":"19d552b5c3e3540690df570ff734d2a5a9edbcd6","tid":494473,"uid":84070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T13:46:42.000Z","msg":"頂番上黎<br />\n聽日就上機<br />\n<br />\n結果前一個星期都係忍唔住想走之前搵你食餐飯<br />\n你開頭話好之後又話突然要出trip<br />\n最後都係見你唔到<br />\n唯有寄望之後番黎會見到你"}]}